威泽饰演的里弗斯·科莫谈论与泰勒·斯威夫特的合作并被誉为她的“音乐英雄” https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezers-rivers-cuomo-talks-working-with-taylor-swift-and-being-hailed-her-musical-hero-3767767?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=威泽斯·里弗斯·科莫谈论与泰勒·斯威夫特合作并被誉为她的音乐英雄Anagricel DuranFri, 21 Jun 2024 19:31:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsPopRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3767767 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 2009 年乐队英雄广告幕后花絮。图片来源：Charley Gallay 和 Kevin Winter via GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “泰勒·斯威夫特非常亲切，当她走进房间并开始与我们交谈时，每个人都爱上了她。她就像一个天生的领导者”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezers-rivers-cuomo-talks-working-with-taylor-swift-and-being-hailed-her-musical-hero-3767767">韦泽 (Weezer) 的里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 谈论与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的合作并被誉为她的“音乐英雄”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 和泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 2009 年乐队英雄广告幕后花絮。图片来源：Charley Gallay 和 Kevin Winter via GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Rivers-Cuomo-and-Taylor-Swift-behind-the-scenes-of-Band-Hero-advert-in-2009.-Credit-Charley-Gallay-and-Kevin-Winter-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Weezer">韦泽</a>的<a href="/artists/Rivers-Cuomo">里弗斯·科莫</a>公开了他与<a href="/artists/Taylor-Swift">泰勒·斯威夫特</a>合作拍摄广告的经历，她称赞他是她的“音乐英雄”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-weezer-rivers-cuomo-3765447">Weezer 的 Rivers Cuomo：“如果泰勒·斯威夫特想要制作一张摇滚专辑，我很乐意帮忙！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>科莫<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/does-rock-n-roll-kill-braincells-weezer-rivers-cuomo-3765447">在本周的<em>《摇滚杀死脑细胞》</em>系列节目中接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，回顾了 2009 年与这位《宝石迷阵》歌手的合作。这则广告是为电子游戏《乐队英雄》拍摄的，其中包括科莫、斯威夫特、《<a href="/artists/Fall-Out-Boy">打倒》</a>等。 <a href="/artists/Fall-Out-Boy">Boy</a>乐队的<a href="/artists/Pete-Wentz">Pete Wentz</a>和<a href="/artists/Blink-182">Blink-182</a>乐队的<a href="/artists/Travis-Barker">Travis Barker</a>重现了<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/tom-cruise">汤姆·克鲁斯</a><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G2UVsyVLLcE">1983 年<em>电影《Risky Business</em> 》中标志性的“旧时光摇滚”舞蹈场景，</a>然后乐队开始表演斯威夫特 2008 年的热门歌曲“Love Story”。</p><p> “电影<em>《危险生意》</em>上映时我还是个十几岁的孩子，所以汤姆·克鲁斯穿着内衣跳舞的场景对我们这一代人来说是标志性的和有影响力的，所以能够与其他几位巨星一起重现这个场景是一种巨大的荣幸， “巴迪·霍利”歌手说道。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特乐队英雄广告" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vHBcGG_9HBk?start=18&#038;feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="危险的商业舞蹈场景" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/G2UVsyVLLcE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“泰勒·斯威夫特非常和蔼可亲，当她走进房间并开始与我们交谈时，每个人都爱上了她。她就像一个天生的领导者。”</p><p>在一次幕后视频采访中谈到广告的创作时，斯威夫特说道：“广告的前提是我们滑进客厅，里面有我和另外三名玩家，另外三名玩家是我的一些音乐英雄。所以当我得知来自 Weezer 的 Travis Barker、Pete Wentz 和 Rivers 正在随着我的歌曲演奏并真正摇滚起来时，我有点害怕。”</p><p>在斯威夫特称赞科莫是她的音乐英雄之一后， <em>《NME》</em>问科莫是否曾讨论过与斯威夫特的合作，科莫回答说：“没有，我们从未谈论过这一点。我从来没有想到过这一点。如果她想制作一张摇滚专辑，我很乐意帮忙！我有预感，我会先接到<a href="/artists/Miley-Cyrus">麦莉赛勒斯</a>的电话！ [笑]那就太酷了。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="泰勒·斯威夫特、特拉维斯·巴克、皮特·温兹和里弗斯·科莫 - BANDHERO" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/LTSh48b1uXo?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在其他新闻中，Weezer 最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezer-reflect-on-30th-anniversary-of-the-blue-album-and-share-original-home-demos-3755348">回顾了《蓝色专辑》30 周年并分享了原创的家庭演示</a>。</p><p>今年晚些时候，乐队将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezer-to-celebrate-30-years-of-debut-album-with-voyage-to-the-blue-planet-tour-with-flaming-lips-and-dinosaur-jr-3599743">开始他们即将到来的“蓝色星球之旅”北美巡演</a>。维泽将在演出中完整播放该唱片，并承诺将提供稀有品和“非常特别的嘉宾”。他们将得到<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-flaming-lips">The Flaming Lips</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dinosaur-jr">Dinosaur Jr.</a>的支持。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fweezer-tickets%2Fartist%2F766591" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>查找剩余的门票。</p><p>在其他地方， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-what-weezer-and-smashing-pumpkins-played-as-they-kicked-off-their-joint-uk-tour-in-birmingham-3763815">Smashing Pumpkins 和 Weezer 本月早些时候在伯明翰开始了他们的联合英国巡演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/weezers-rivers-cuomo-talks-working-with-taylor-swift-and-being-hailed-her-musical-hero-3767767">韦泽 (Weezer) 的里弗斯·科莫 (Rivers Cuomo) 谈论与泰勒·斯威夫特 (Taylor Swift) 的合作并被誉为她的“音乐英雄”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 《牛肉》第二季可能是奥斯卡·伊萨克和凯瑞·穆里根在《驾驶》中的重聚https://www.nme.com/news/tv/beef-season-two-could-be-drive-reuinion-oscar-isaac-carey-mulligan-3767762?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=beef-season-two-可能是奥斯卡·艾萨克·凯里·穆里根的驾驶重聚Alex BerryFri, 21 Jun 2024 19:05:18 +0000 NewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3767762 <p><img width="1532" height="973" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯瑞·穆里根 奥斯卡·伊萨克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac.jpg 1532w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1532px) 100vw, 1532px" /></p><p>据报道，两人正在“协商出演”第二季</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/beef-season-two-could-be-drive-reuinion-oscar-isaac-carey-mulligan-3767762">《牛肉》第二季可能是奥斯卡·伊萨克和凯瑞·穆里根在《驾驶》中的重聚，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="1532" height="973" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="凯瑞·穆里根 奥斯卡·伊萨克" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac.jpg 1532w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/carey-mulligan-Oscar-Isaac-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1532px) 100vw, 1532px" /></p><p>关于<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/beef"><em>《牛肉》</em></a>第二季演员阵容的传言已经开始，据报道，第二季可能会看到两位前搭档的重聚。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-best-tv-shows-of-2023-so-far-3467418">2023 年最佳电视节目……到目前为止！</a></strong></li></ul><p> A24/Netflix 推出的剧集讲述了路怒症争吵升级为全面争执的故事，其第一季就获得了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/the-75th-emmy-awards-full-list-of-winners-2024-3570870">好评</a>，赢得了八项艾美奖和三项金球奖。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/beef-season-2-reportedly-eyeing-jake-gyllenhaal-and-anne-hathaway-3593424">今年早些时候宣布</a>第二季可能会出现，最初有传言称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jake-gyllenhaal">杰克·吉伦哈尔</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anne-hathaway">安妮·海瑟薇</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/priscilla"><em>普里西拉</em></a>饰演的卡莉·斯派尼都会参与其中。</p><p>现在，据<em><a href="https://deadline.com/2024/06/beef-oscar-isaac-carey-mulligan-season-2-1235979489/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Deadline</a>报道，</em>另外两名好莱坞一线明星可能会加入演员阵容，有消息称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oscar-isaac">奥斯卡·伊萨克</a>和凯瑞·穆里根可能会在第二季中主演。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="牛肉|先睹为快独家剪辑：煽动事件| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0WEYoGJJYVk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这将标志着两位演员的再次重聚，他们曾与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ryan-gosling">瑞恩·高斯林</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bryan-cranston">布莱恩·科兰斯顿</a>一起出演 2011 年动作惊悚片<em>《亡命驾驶》</em>以及 2013 年传记片《<em>醉乡民谣》</em> 。</p><p>据报道，内部消息人士告诉<em>Deadline</em> ，两人正在“协商出演”第二季，而穆里根和艾萨克的角色原本是为海瑟薇和吉伦哈尔准备的。</p><p>据<em>Deadline</em>报道，第二季尚未正式获得批准，但内部消息人士透露，该剧的剧情将围绕两对不和的夫妻展开。</p><p>这一传言是在穆里根忙碌了一年之后传出的。穆里根在<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/saltburn"><em>《索尔特本》</em></a>中饰演裴淳华饰演的古怪朋友，在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bradley-cooper">布莱德利·库珀</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/maestro"><em>《大师</em></a>》中饰演伦纳德·伯恩斯坦的妻子费利西亚·蒙泰莱格雷，获得奥斯卡提名，并与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/adam-sandler">亚当·桑德勒</a>演对手戏。在 Netflix 科幻电影<em>《太空人》</em>中。</p><p>艾萨克过去的作品包括丹尼斯·维伦纽夫的《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/star-wars"><em>星球大战</em></a>》续集三部曲《<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/dune"><em>沙丘</em></a>》，并在<em>《醉乡戴维斯》</em>中扮演同名角色，为他赢得了金球奖提名，目前他正在拍摄<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guillermo-del-toro">吉列尔莫·德尔·托罗</a>的<em>《弗兰肯斯坦》</em> ，他在片中扮演弗兰肯斯坦博士。他还因在 HBO 迷你剧《<em>婚姻场景》</em>中与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jessica-chastain">杰西卡·查斯坦</a>演对手戏而获得艾美奖和金球奖提名。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/beef-season-two-could-be-drive-reuinion-oscar-isaac-carey-mulligan-3767762">《牛肉》第二季可能是奥斯卡·伊萨克和凯瑞·穆里根在《驾驶》中的重聚，并</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
